□ Distribute closed-source modifications
□ Keep your customizations proprietary
□ Profit financially from VibedTracker

You can use the AGPL v3 (FREE) license if you:
□ Use VibedTracker for personal/educational purposes only
□ Share all modifications under AGPL v3
□ Don't offer VibedTracker as a paid service
□ Are an individual developer or non-profit organization

If unsure, please contact: stefan@vibedtracker.de

